data.description: **Stunning Attached Home with Two-Car Garage - New Price Reduction to $750,000 - Just in Time for the Holidays or Perfect for the Investor Looking to Deposit That Cash Before Year End**Discover the perfect home for your family or investment portfolio! This immaculate attached home, nestled in a desirable neighborhood, now offers a fantastic opportunity. Offering a perfect blend of comfort, elegance, and modern design, this property has been thoughtfully remodeled with the finest materials, making it a true gem in the market.**Key Features:**- **Centrally Located**: This home is conveniently situated near numerous attractions and amenities. It's just a stone's throw away from CSU Dominguez Hills, offering educational opportunities at your doorstep. The South Bay Pavilion, Dignity Sports Park, Victoria Golf Course, and Harbor UCLA Hospital are all easily accessible, ensuring you have entertainment, recreation, and healthcare options within reach.- **Spacious Layout**: With a generous 1,498 square feet of living space, this home provides ample room for your family to spread out and enjoy.- **4 Bedrooms**: The property features four beautifully appointed bedrooms. One of them is conveniently located on the main floor, alongside a 3/4 bathroom, making it perfect for guests, in-laws, or those seeking single-level living.- **2 Bathrooms**: Both bathrooms have been completely remodeled, showcasing high-end finishes and fixtures.- **Exquisite Finishes**: No detail has been spared in the renovation of this home. You'll find top-of-the-line materials throughout, including elegant quartz countertops and a matching backsplash that grace the kitchen.- **Brand New Appliances**: The kitchen is equipped with state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances, offering a stylish and functional space for culinary enthusiasts.- **Efficient Air and HVAC System**: Stay comfortable year-round with a new air and HVAC system that ensures optimal temperature control and energy efficiency.- **Elegant Flooring**: The entire home features engineered hardwood flooring, providing both durability and a touch of luxury.- **Two-Car Garage**: The garage is more than just a parking space; it has been thoughtfully finished with drywall and recessed lighting, creating a versatile space for projects, storage, or simply protecting your vehicles.- **Low Maintenance Landscaping**: The exterior of the home features low maintenance landscaping, ensuring your weekends are spent relaxing rather than landscaping.- **Lot Size**: The property sits on a 3,489 square foot lot, providing enough outdoor space for outdoor activities, gardening, or enjoying the fresh air. This meticulously updated home offers a seamless blend of contemporary design and practical functionality. It's perfect for families seeking a comfortable and stylish place to call home, with all the modern conveniences you desire. Don't miss this opportunity to make this home your own. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and secure your piece of luxury living.
